title: Navigon Europe Q1 2009 MN7 maps
description:
NAVIGON Europa Release Q1_2009 Map for PDA and PNA

Following countries are included:
Albania, Andorra, Belarus, Belgium, Bosnia-Herzegovina, Bulgaria, Denmark, Germany, Estonia, Finland, France, Gibraltar, Greece, United Kingdom,
Isle of Man, Ireland , Italy, Croatia, Latvia, Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg,FYROM (Mazedonien ), Monte Carlo, Montenegro, Netherlands,
Norway, Austria, Poland, Portugal, Romania, San Marino, Sweden, Switzerland, Serbia, Slovakia, Slovenia, Spain, Czech Republic, Hungary, Vatican


Requirements: Navigon MN 7.3.4 PNA and 7.3.1 PDA + PNA


Works on PNA aswell as PDA*


*PDA users: use old q4_2008 files for  Navigon -> Settings -> Core


Everything should work smoothly, in case of some error you can overwrite your settings with the ones included in the seperate rar.

NJOY and LEAVE thanks if U like it :)
